# directive-no-args

## Input

```
#standalone
key value

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..22
  DIRECTIVE@0..11
    SHARP@0..1 "#"
    WORD@1..11 "standalone"
    LINE_STRING@11..11
      STRING@11..11 ""
  NEWLINE@11..12 "\n"
  ENTRY@12..22
    WORD_KEY@12..15
      WORD@12..15 "key"
    SPACE@15..16 " "
    LINE_STRING@16..21
      STRING@16..21 "value"
    NEWLINE@21..22 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Directive {
            sharp: SHARP@0..1 "#",
            name: WORD@1..11 "standalone",
            args: LineString {
                string: STRING@11..11 "",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@12..15 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@16..21 "value",
            },
        },
    ],
}
```

